UPDATE companies SET agent_ids_notes = 'Received from Rahul - 2026-03-13: Building in Fintech - PFM with a great wedge. This is a short blurb: CA sees taxes, not investments.  Broker sees investments, not liabilities.  Bank sees balances, not goals. India''s 2 crore ₹30L+ income households have three advisors and no one who owns the outcome. Command is that entity. A personal finance agent that unifies accounts, loans, taxes, and investments and converts the full picture into proactive, executable actions. Before you ask. India''s Account Aggregator framework makes unified financial data real. AI makes continuous personalised optimisation possible. The financial rails are live. We''re building above every bank, broker, and insurer in India, the default decision layer for the end customer, the operating system for personal finance. Ankur Garg (Ex- Great Learning, Capital One, Morgan Stanley), Varun Gupta (Ex- Embibe, Ola, Linkedin) ---' WHERE id = 98 AND (agent_ids_notes IS NULL OR agent_ids_notes = '');
